---
/**
 * Intro - seção "An independent web design and branding agency"
 * Atributos: Innovations, Excellence, Creativity, etc.
 */
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-dark-700">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-8">
        An independent web design and branding agency in Manchester
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg">
        We believe a website isn't just a digital presence — it's a powerful tool that tells your story. We have industry experience, and win awards.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-2 text-white/70">
        <span>Innovations</span>
        <span>Competence</span>
        <span>Excellence</span>
        <span>Web design</span>
        <span>Creativity</span>
        <span>Development</span>
        <span>Experience</span>
        <span>Branding</span>
        <span>Passion</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
